175 A.3d 159 SCOTT VALENTINE, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. MAXIMO ALMANZAR AND ANA ALMANZAR, DEFENDANTS-RESPONDENTS.

C-238 September Term 2017

079685 October 26, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002207-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
